org.bonitasoft.engine.identity

Class UserCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.identity.UserCreator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class UserCreator
extends Object
implements Serializable
    represents a helper for creating User. Chaining is possible with this creator to ease the User creation.
    For instance, new UserCreator("john.doe", "password").setFirstname("John").setLastname("Doe");
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte
    See Also:
    User, Serialized Form
